  group_by(name, set) %>% 
  summarize(Ayes = sum(vote)) %>%
  tidyr::spread(key = set, value = Ayes) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = First_Half, y = Second_Half)) +

  select(-name) %>% 
  svd()

  as.data.frame()

  voters %>% 
  kmeans(centers = 6)

  voters %>%
